text: Pulaali'i Tuiteleleapaga Iuli Nikolao Pula (born December 31, 1955) is an American Samoan politician. He has been the 9th and current governor of American Samoa since 2025. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Living people Category:Governors of American Samoa Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:1955 births
title: Pula Nikolao Pula
